XPath
1. Absolute Path (/)
2. Relative Path(//)
1. Absolute Path
     Root to current Object
Relative Xpath can contain:
1. Arithmetic Operator
2. Xpath Functions()
    text()
    contains()
    starts-with()
    normalize space()
    
    JavascriptExecutor
    
   1. Identify the object using JavaScript +Execute the script using Java Script
   2. Identify object using WebDriver + Execute the script using Java Script
   
   1. Scroll / ScrollTO
   2. ScrollBy
   3. ScrrollIntoView
