   TestNG 
   
   Assertion:
    1. HardAssertion(Assert)
    2. SoftAssertion(SoftAssert)
   *********************************************************************
   Framework
   1. TestNg Framework
   2. POM design Pattern
   3. PageFactory class for locating the objects in the application
   4. Approach Data Driven (Data Provider)
   5. Default TestNG Report
   6. Log4j (For Logging purpose)
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   